<div class="tw-px-4 tw-py-3 tw-rounded tw-mb-4 tw-bg-gray-100 tw-border tw-border-gray-400 tw-text-gray-700 tw-flex tw-relative" role="alert" data-controller="alert">
  <i class="fa fa-info-circle tw-me-2 fa-2x"></i>
  <div>
    <p>
      <strong>
        Welcome to the Ayah recitations segment tool
      </strong>
    </p>

    <p>
      Segment/timestamps for each word are typically generated using machine learning. This tool allows us to preview the highlighting and refine or correct edge cases to ensure accuracy.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you'd like to contribute to <%= @resource.name %>, simply click the link below to request access from the admin. Once approved, you'll be able to correct and improve the segments for <%= @resource.name %>.
    </p>

    <p id="btn-request-permission">
      <%= link_to 'Request Access', '_', class: 'tw-px-4 tw-py-2 tw-text-sm tw-font-medium tw-bg-gray-800 hover:tw-bg-gray-900 tw-text-white tw-rounded tw-transition-colors',  data: { controller: 'ajax-modal', url: new_user_project_path(resource_id: @resource.id, modal: true), css_class: 'modal-lg'} %>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>